text: FX is a Finnish pay television owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel launched on 23 May 2010 but was replaced by Discovery Home & Health on 20 September 2012. The channel started broadcasting in 16:9 aspect ratio on 19 September 2013. On 31 March 2023, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that Discovery Home & Health in Finland would be relaunched as FX on 11 June 2023. == Logos == file:FX International logo.svg|23 May 2010-20 September 2012 file:Discovery H&H.png;|20 September 2012-11 June 2023 file:FX Logo 2023.svg|11 June 2023-present Category:Television channels in Europe
